data.description:
This is the one  you have been waiting for----it is ready for your pickiest buyers and it is priced to sell!!This home also sits at the end of the street with a gorgeous shade tree and front patio perfect for morning coffees. A BEAUTIFUL HOME IN A WONDERFUL COMMUNITY!!  This amazing home offers an open concept with plenty of space to live and work. With a large dining room, surrounded by tall ceilings and the "awe"  factor, all  making  this the home you fall IN LOVE with. Light streams in and  the purposefully designed  floor plan accommodates so many life styles (needs)  A gorgeous entryway,  main floor master and room to grow! ! This highly sought after Ranch is located  on a corner lot with a partially finished basement (the  bedroom is completed)  and all of the "must have's"  The are numerous upgrades and the updated finishes/appliances!) include  big ticket items ----roof, furnace, water softener. The "newer"  appliances  showcase the refrigerator, dishwasher, oven and microwave . The backyard is a sanctuary & has an amazing patio for friends and fun, ! Walking paths that are in close vicinity and so much more to offer.  In close proximity to all of the major arteries for commuting. 
A MUST SEE
